Business leaders from Kenya and Tanzania met today to deliberate on how best to further trade relations between the two countries. The forum which comprised of private and public sector players from both countries &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; underscored that value addition and removal of non?tariff barriers will go a long way in cementing trade relations. Ktn`s Noah Kipkemboi has been closely following the trade talks.
